OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be mainly dry but becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy. Then the rest of
OL,8,Fthe night will be cloudy with
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain spreading northeast,
OL,10,Foccasionally heavy in the southwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FLargeyl cloudy morning with
OL,13,Fsome rain. Variable amounts of cloud
OL,14,Fand sunny spells in the afternoon
OL,15,Falong with scattered slow moving
OL,16,Fshowers, occasionally heavy. West
OL,17,Fcoast drier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
